snippet.title: Harry Wolff
snippet.description:
Hello there and welcome to my channel!

My name is Harry Wolff and I love JavaScript.

So! Every week I post a new video to share my love and joy of JavaScript and all things web related.

I come with over 10 years of industry experience so I like to think I know what I'm talking about.

Glad to have you here!
